---

<Layout
  title="Life at Levein - Levein Group"
  description="Discover what it's like to work at Levein Group. Explore our company culture, employee stories, and the vibrant work environment that makes us a great place to build your career. Join us and be part of a team that values innovation, growth, and making a positive impact in the tech and healthcare industries."
>
  <Hero
    title="A place to grow and pursue your passions."
    description="Flexibility is a strategic advantage. Adopting a remote-first mindset boosted productivity and expanded our global talent pool."
  />

  <section
    class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 bg-white font-sans"
