    <div
      class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row justify-between items-start lg:items-end gap-6 mb-16"
    >
      <h2
        class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-primary font-medium text-gray-900 tracking-tight"
      >
        Life at Levein
      </h2>
      <p
        class="text-levein-black text-[16px] md:text-base max-w-md leading-relaxed lg:text-left"
      >
        It’s not all work and no play – fun is an integral part of our culture.
        Both competitive and non-competitive events are organized by an in-house
        committee.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-4 md:gap-6">
